{"tid":821157,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"香港原創既中世紀攻城策略boardgame 上線喔","createTime":"2018-09-15T21:34:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-16T01:54:31.000Z","uid":195137,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"cea1da8ed14e1e0fc9f2ce5c3a9677127c4396e0","tid":821157,"uid":195137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T21:34:10.000Z","msg":"大家仲記唔記得一兩個月前我地出個post 問大家意見，之前條link 係度: <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/747482/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/747482/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\nUnrecorded Siege 係一幅中度策略遊戲，故事係講中世紀百年戰爭中間有一段未被記錄既攻城戰。唔止得一個玩法，我地造左好多唔同既戰役包括單人模式，一打一攻城，四人混戰同串連起唔同戰役概Legacy mode，各有各既故事同勝利條件。上次俾大家睇左啲成品圖，而今次有好詳盡既圖去介紹我地既流程玩法:<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">首先係選擇陣營</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">法國同英國目有概兵種組合唔同，玩法都唔同。一邊用卡，一邊角色。</span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/16/044903_aef68fa503f788855f502ca1e5351d74.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F16%2F044903_aef68fa503f788855f502ca1e5351d74.jpg&h=a0d346e4&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">通常每回合主要都會有8個階段，根據唔同戰役會有小量分別。</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://ctelroy.com/unrecorded_siege/unre_phase_GIF.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fctelroy.com%2Funrecorded_siege%2Funre_phase_GIF.gif&h=3dee5920&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">根據陣形同玩法，睇下係回合入面完唔完成到目標，包括攻守城，收集資源，護送，佔特定地方等，核心流程大概就係咁。</div><br />\n<br />\n如果覺得唔吸引，唔好插得太大力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n是咁的，其實我地仲有幾日就會上Kickstarter，9月20號。 係之前我地想搞個giveaway， 抽中左既巴絲打梗係會有一盒Game啦，而且係Collection Pack， 會有角色模型。具體係每100個正評，就會係呢個post 度抽一個留左言既巴絲打。當kickstart 到100%，就會送番一副成品俾中獎既大家!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果大家想試玩，可以上我地facebook約我地或者黎Join我地概試玩會，緊kickstarter期間會搞幾次。<br />\n<br />\nFB:<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/UnreSiege/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FUnreSiege%2F&d=%2B%2FnptQ0%2FuxgwkMZWLxwQQoS5T71%2BpEKm9yZKOKwCwR4%3D&h=85e23276\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/UnreSiege/</a><br />\nIG：<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/unresiege/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Funresiege%2F&d=%2B%2FnptQ0%2FuxgwkMZWLxwQQoS5T71%2BpEKm9yZKOKwCwR4%3D&h=5842dc87\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/unresiege/</a>"},{"pid":"a971672f27cb0c284e880baad14127b461f353ab","tid":821157,"uid":134019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T23:17:34.000Z","msg":"留名，會backup既<br />\n希望唔好好似間世界評議會2咁<br />\n走左數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9828c20a57a6fba34316e0f76415d614f071f439","tid":821157,"uid":166237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T23:23:52.000Z","msg":"留明 支持本地創作"},{"pid":"a951f4e061121aecec37a7dec9f1f7add3eb322f","tid":821157,"uid":72424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T23:34:55.000Z","msg":"暫時未睇得明點玩 不過都想試下"},{"pid":"bf61e58ca2dae338e8713b66ea6a982526357003","tid":821157,"uid":195137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a971672f27cb0c284e880baad14127b461f353ab","tid":821157,"uid":134019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T23:17:34.000Z","msg":"留名，會backup既<br />\n希望唔好好似間世界評議會2咁<br />\n走左數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T00:46:48.000Z","msg":"放心，唔會走數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBG地方我地老是常出現，露晒臉，唔敢走數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8a85a8ab139de63254a18738be